The paper deals with an age of information minimization problem in the context of multiple flows of update packets sent over multiple servers. This problem is related to information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
